metadata.name: 2021 running champion
metadata.description:
It is the photograph that won the 2nd prize in 2021 in the running marathon competition held every year in Turkey.
The starting point was also taken in the 15-kilometer running area. It is a very difficult photo to take with Zoom in photography technique.

Photographer: Metin INAN Collection Name: life and marathon Date: 20.02.2021 Original size:8256 × 5504 pixels 300 dpi Original Format: RAW Print: 1/1 Location: Trabzon / Turkey

My photography equipment: Body: NIKON D850 Lenses: NIKON 14-24mm 2.8 , NIKON 24-70mm 2.8, NIKON 70-200mm 2.8
